const onlyWithFillStyle = [IconsData.coin, IconsData.theme];
const onlyWithLineStyle = [
    IconsData.pulse,
    IconsData.check,
    IconsData.add,
    IconsData.close,
    IconsData.subtract,
    IconsData.fullscreen,
    IconsData.arrowLeftSfirst,
    IconsData.arrowRightSLast,
    IconsData.frArrowLeftS,
    IconsData.frArrowRightS
];
const withLineDoubleStyle = [IconsData.frArrowLeftS, IconsData.frArrowRightS];
const withoutstyle = [
    IconsData.alignLeft,
    IconsData.fullscreen,
    IconsData.codeView,
    IconsData.fontSize,
    IconsData.bold,
    IconsData.highlight,
    IconsData.h1,
    IconsData.h2,
    IconsData.h3,
    IconsData.h4,
    IconsData.h5,
    IconsData.h6,
    IconsData.hashtag,
    IconsData.italic,
    IconsData.link,
    IconsData.linkUnlink,
    IconsData.listOrdered,
    IconsData.listUnordered,
    IconsData.questionMark,
    IconsData.separator,
    IconsData.space,
    IconsData.subscript,
    IconsData.superscript,
    IconsData.table2,
    IconsData.translate2
];

type IconsKey = keyof typeof IconsData;
export type Icons = typeof IconsData[IconsKey];
export type IconStyle = "fill" | "line";

export class Icon {
    public static get(iconName: Icons, style: IconStyle = "fill") {
        if (withoutstyle.includes(iconName as any)) {
            return `fr-icon-${iconName}`;
        } else {
            const iconStyle = Icon.getStyle(iconName, style);
            return `fr-icon-${iconName}-${iconStyle}`;
        }
    }

    private static getStyle(iconName: Icons, style: IconStyle): IconStyle | "line-double" {
        if (onlyWithFillStyle.includes(iconName as any) && style === "line") {
            return (style = "fill");
        } else if (onlyWithLineStyle.includes(iconName as any) && style === "fill") {
            return (style = "line");
        }
        if (style === "line" && withLineDoubleStyle.includes(iconName as any)) {
            return "line-double";
        } else {
            return style;
        }
    }
}
